snippet.description:
Warner Brothers Replacing Amber Heard With This Actress If She Loses At Trial
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
New Channel | Top 10 Central DARK: https://bit.ly/32k64cW

Warner Brothers is waiting for the outcome of the defamation trial between johnny and amber to decide if they are going to replace her in Aquaman 2. Rumor has it that Several names of actresses have been put forward, including Emilia Clarke, Blake Lively. But sources who spoke to we got this covered say that Emily blunt is being considered by Warner Brothers as a replacement if they need to get rid of her due to an unfavorable outcome of the trial and all the bad press.
